==============================================================================
rpcb_data.csv  -  Reproducibility Project: Cancer Biology
==============================================================================
Source:   Errington, T. M., Mathur, M., Soderberg, C. K., Denis, A.,
          Perfito, N., Iorns, E., & Nosek, B. A. (2021). Investigating the
          replicability of preclinical cancer biology. eLife, 10, e71601.
          https://doi.org/10.7554/eLife.71601
OSF:      https://osf.io/e5nvr/  (umbrella: https://osf.io/e81xl/)
License:  Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0).
          https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/legalcode

Required attribution: Errington et al. (2021), eLife 10:e71601, used under
CC BY 4.0. No modifications were made to the underlying values; columns were
selected and renamed for compatibility with the eJAB analysis schema
(study_id, p, n, q).
